-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.
SELECT * FROM default.pune_pollutants_contours live WHERE observationDateTime in (SELECT MAX(observationDateTime) from default.pune_pollutants_contours live)
-- where observationdatetime >=  ((date_add('minute', 330, localtimestamp)) - interval '1' hour)

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.
SELECT primary_key,airQualityLevel,deviceStatus, live.id, observationDateTime, airQualityIndex, aqiMajorPollutant, relativeHumidity, atmosphericPressure, co2, pm2p5, uv, o3, airTemperature, no2, co, pm10, illuminance, so2, ambientNoise, latitude, longitude, address
FROM default.pune_aqm_live live inner join default.pune_sensor_coordinates sensors on live.id=sensors.id
-- where observationdatetime >=  ((date_add('minute', 330, localtimestamp)) - interval '1' hour)
